Supplied in a 15M coil, this insulation has very low thermal conductivity alongside high levels of resistance to water vapour transmission, helping to reduce energy losses during the long term while also minimising moisture ingress and reducing the risk of corrosion under insulation (CUI). Suitable for installation in public buildings and for use in process industries, AF Evo has inbuilt antimicrobial protection and high levels of fire performance make it a reliable choice for even the most challenging of situations. In addition to insulation, the AF/Armaflex range includes fire sleeves, pipe supports and adhesives for a comprehensive single-brand solution.

Description: Offering flexible and reliable condensation control, AF/ArmaFlex Evo 1/2" OD x 1/2" WT pipe insulation is designed with a unique microcell structure for easy installation with no need for an additional vapour barrier. Supplied in a 15M coil, this insulation has very low thermal conductivity alongside high levels of resistance to water vapour transmission, helping to reduce energy losses during the long term while also minimising moisture ingress and reducing the risk of corrosion under insulation (CUI). Suitable for installation in public buildings and for use in process industries, AF Evo has inbuilt antimicrobial protection and high levels of fire performance make it a reliable choice for even the most challenging of situations. In addition to insulation, the AF/Armaflex range includes fire sleeves, pipe supports and adhesives for a comprehensive single-brand solution.

Supplied in a 15M coil, this insulation has very low thermal conductivity alongside high levels of resistance to water vapour transmission, helping to reduce energy losses during the long term while also minimising moisture ingress and reducing the risk of corrosion under insulation (CUI). Suitable for installation in public buildings and for use in process industries, AF Evo has inbuilt antimicrobial protection and high levels of fire performance make it a reliable choice for even the most challenging of situations. In addition to insulation, the AF/Armaflex range includes fire sleeves, pipe supports and adhesives for a comprehensive single-brand solution.

Title: Armaflex Class 0 sheet insulation 3/8" Black
Description: This Armaflex Class 0 10mm insulation sheet is made of an elastomeric foam based on synthetic rubber and supplied in a 2M length. A flexible, closed-cell nitrile rubber insulation material, Class 0 has high water vapour diffusion resistance and low thermal conductivity, prevents condensation and reduces energy loss while protecting pipes, air ducts, and vessels from frost. ArmaFlex Class 0 is suitable for use on hot and cold water services, chilled water lines, heating systems, air conditioning ductwork, refrigerated pipework, process and industrial pipework and equipment.
